## Banque de prompts vidéo

5 mouvements vidéo typiques pour les vidéos immobilières haut de gamme.

### Mouvement 01 — Travelling d'entrée

```text
Duration: 4s
Use first-frame.png as start frame, last-frame.png as end frame.

Camera: slow forward tracking shot through the entrance.
Motion: door opens slightly or camera moves past the doorway into the living space, revealing warm natural light and architectural depth.
Lighting: soft natural light, consistent and warm.
Style: cinematic, 24fps, film grain, color graded.
```

### Mouvement 02 — Reveal du salon

```text
Duration: 5s
Use first-frame.png as start frame, last-frame.png as end frame.

Camera: slow lateral tracking shot from left to right.
Motion: living room gradually reveals its full volume, windows and view. Curtains move subtly with natural air.
Lighting: natural daylight remains soft and consistent.
Style: cinematic, 24fps, film grain, color graded.
```

### Mouvement 03 — Détail matière

```text
Duration: 3s
Use first-frame.png as start frame, last-frame.png as end frame.

Camera: slow macro push in.
Motion: light glides across the premium material, revealing texture of marble, wood, brass or stone. No other movement.
Lighting: warm side light, consistent.
Style: cinematic, 24fps, film grain, color graded.
```

### Mouvement 04 — Terrasse vers vue

```text
Duration: 5s
Use first-frame.png as start frame, last-frame.png as end frame.

Camera: slow push forward from terrace interior toward the view.
Motion: camera moves past outdoor furniture toward the skyline, sea or garden. Light curtains or plants move subtly in the wind.
Lighting: golden hour slowly softening into evening.
Style: cinematic, 24fps, film grain, color graded.
```

### Mouvement 05 — Piscine blue hour

```text
Duration: 5s
Use first-frame.png as start frame, last-frame.png as end frame.

Camera: very slow pull back.
Motion: pool water moves gently, warm lights turn more visible in the villa, reflections become deeper as the sky darkens.
Lighting: blue hour ambience with warm interior glow.
Style: cinematic, 24fps, film grain, color graded.
```

